==Arabic==

===Etymology===
From the root verb {{ARchar|[[علم]]}} (ʕálima), to [[know]], to have [[knowledge]].

===Adjective===
'''{{ARchar|اعلم}}''' (áʕlam)

#''([[elative]] of'' {{ARchar|[[عالم]]}}): having more [[knowledge]]; more [[learned]].
#:*{{ARchar|[[الله اعلم]]}} (Alláhu áʕlam) &mdash; ''God knows best.''

